   Minor Sports Offer Opportunity for Would-Be Owners
   ---
   Businessman Hopes to Fly High on the
   Wings of a Cycle-League Franchise
   ----
   By Dave Kansas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/16/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<MS>
